<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīsōdarasya paripūrṇnasudhākarasya vaṁśē calukya<unclear>nara</unclear>nādhaparaṁparābhūt <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīrājarājanṛpatērvvijayasta
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>tō</unclear>bhūtcrīrājarājanṛpatē<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>vvijeyakṣitīśaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1*] nirmmāyārāmarēkhāṁ vividhatarulatāsaṁcayaissaptagō
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dātīraṁ sarvvaṁ śilābhiptatakanakadalairbhbhīmanāthāla<unclear>yā</unclear>graṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> datvāsaubhānunāmnā puramapi sukarā<unclear>ḍyā</unclear>grahārēṣu
<lb n="4"/>saddyaḥ sa<unclear>ṁ</unclear>krāṁtau pauravīṭyaṁtavanidhiracanāṁ krotta<unclear>mā</unclear>vāsyayātrāṁ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2*] bhīmēśasyajagadgurōrabhinavaṁ māghā
