<lb n="6" break="no"/><unclear>rā</unclear>maitāṁbikāyā mahīnāthastarkkamaṇīṁdubhūmigaṇitē <unclear>ramyē</unclear> śakābdē ghanaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3*] triṁśatā gaṇita
<lb n="7" break="no"/>khaṁḍukairmmitāṁ tāṁḍipa<unclear>ṛti</unclear>viṣayē su<unclear>śōbhi</unclear>nīṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kōnamallanṛpatēḥ krayārjjitāṁ sōpyadāduci
<lb n="8" break="no"/>tatā<unclear>vya</unclear>yāyaca [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4*] 
